---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import GeoPricing from '../components/GeoPricing.astro';

const siteUrl = Astro.site?.href || Astro.url.origin;
const pageUrl = `${siteUrl}/geo`;
---

<Layout 
	title="GEO Services - Generative Engine Optimization for AI Search | InfraDev Consulting" 
	description="Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) services for AI-powered search engines and generative AI systems. Optimize your content for ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, and other generative AI platforms. Capture AI agent traffic and synthetic search results."
	canonical={pageUrl}
>
	<Header />
	<main itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Service">
		<section class="geo-hero section">
			<div class="container">
				<nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="breadcrumb">
					<ol>
						<li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
						<li><a href="/brochure">Search Optimization</a></li>
						<li>Generative Engine Optimization</li>
					</ol>
				</nav>
				<div class="hero-content">
					<p class="eyebrow">Generative Engine Optimization</p>
					<h1 itemprop="name">Optimize for Generative AI Search Engines</h1>
					<p class="hero-subtitle">
						As generative AI systems like ChatGPT, Claude, and Gemini become primary search interfaces, your content needs to be optimized for how these systems generate, synthesize, and present information. GEO ensures your business is discoverable and cited by AI agents and generative search platforms.
					</p>
					<div class="hero-cta">
						<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a GEO Consultation</a>
						<a href="#what-is-geo" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="what-is-geo" class="what-is section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>What is Generative Engine Optimization (GEO)?</h2>
					<p>Generative Engine Optimization is the practice of optimizing your content to be discovered, understood, and cited by generative AI systems that create new content based on web sources.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="content-grid">
					<div class="content-card">
						<h3>The Rise of Generative AI Search</h3>
						<p>Traditional search engines return links. Generative AI systems create new content—synthesizing information from multiple sources to generate original responses. GEO optimizes your content to be one of those sources that generative AI systems learn from and cite.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="content-card">
						<h3>Why GEO Matters</h3>
						<p>Millions of users now use ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, and other generative AI systems as their primary search interface. These systems generate responses by learning from web content. If your content isn't optimized for generative AI discovery and understanding, you're invisible to this growing user base.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="content-card">
						<h3>GEO vs. AEO vs. SEO</h3>
						<p>SEO optimizes for traditional search rankings. AEO optimizes for answer engines that extract and cite sources. GEO optimizes for generative AI systems that learn from, synthesize, and create new content based on your information. Each requires different optimization strategies.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="resource-link-box">
					<p><strong>Want to learn more about GEO?</strong> Read our comprehensive guide: <a href="/resources/what-is-geo">What is Generative Engine Optimization (GEO)?</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="why-now section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Why GEO is Essential for AI-Driven Search</h2>
					<p>The future of search is generative</p>
				</div>
				<div class="stats-grid">
					<div class="stat-card">
						<div class="stat-number">100M+</div>
						<div class="stat-label">weekly active users on ChatGPT alone</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-card">
						<div class="stat-number">50%+</div>
						<div class="stat-label">of knowledge workers use AI for research</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-card">
						<div class="stat-number">3x</div>
						<div class="stat-label">growth in AI agent usage year-over-year</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-card">
						<div class="stat-number">70%+</div>
						<div class="stat-label">of generative AI responses synthesize multiple sources</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="insight-box">
					<h3>The Shift</h3>
					<p>Users are increasingly asking AI systems to research, compare, analyze, and synthesize information rather than clicking through search results. Generative AI systems need high-quality, well-structured content to learn from. GEO ensures your content is optimized for AI learning and synthesis, making it more likely to be included in generated responses.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="what-we-do section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>What Our GEO Services Include</h2>
					<p>Comprehensive optimization for generative AI systems</p>
				</div>
				<div class="services-grid">
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>AI Training Data Optimization</h3>
						<p>Optimize your content to be included in AI training datasets. We structure content with clear patterns, consistent formatting, and comprehensive coverage that AI systems can easily learn from and reference.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Semantic Richness Enhancement</h3>
						<p>Enhance content with rich semantic meaning, context, and relationships. Generative AI systems need to understand not just facts, but how concepts relate to each other. We optimize for semantic understanding.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Comprehensive Topic Coverage</h3>
						<p>Create comprehensive content that covers topics in depth. Generative AI systems prefer sources that provide complete, authoritative coverage rather than fragmented information. We ensure your content is comprehensive.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Citation Optimization</h3>
						<p>Structure content to be easily citable by generative AI systems. This includes clear attribution, source links, data citations, and formats that AI systems recognize as authoritative and trustworthy.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Multi-Modal Content Optimization</h3>
						<p>Optimize for AI systems that process text, images, tables, and structured data. We ensure your content works across all modalities that generative AI systems can understand and synthesize.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>AI Agent Discovery</h3>
						<p>Optimize for AI agents and autonomous systems that search the web to answer questions. As AI agents become more common, GEO ensures your content is discoverable and usable by these systems.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Conversational Context Optimization</h3>
						<p>Optimize content for conversational AI interactions. Generative AI systems often need to understand context, follow-up questions, and multi-turn conversations. We structure content to support these interactions.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Generative AI Platform Monitoring</h3>
						<p>Track when and how your content appears in generative AI responses across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, and other platforms. Monitor citations, mentions, and synthesis of your content.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="benefits section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Benefits of Generative Engine Optimization</h2>
					<p>Why GEO is critical for modern search visibility</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefits-grid">
					<div class="benefit-card">
						<h3>Capture AI Agent Traffic</h3>
						<p>Be discoverable by AI agents and autonomous systems that search the web. As AI agents become more common, GEO ensures your content is accessible to these systems.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-card">
						<h3>Future-Proof Your Content Strategy</h3>
						<p>As generative AI becomes the dominant search interface, GEO ensures your content remains discoverable and valuable. Traditional SEO alone won't be sufficient.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-card">
						<h3>Brand Visibility in AI Responses</h3>
						<p>Even when users don't click through, appearing in generative AI responses builds brand awareness and authority. GEO maximizes your visibility in AI-generated content.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-card">
