						<p>Optimize for Perplexity's AI search engine that generates answers with citations. We structure content to be easily cited and synthesized by Perplexity's generative AI.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="platform-card">
						<h3>AI Agents & Bots</h3>
						<p>Optimize for AI agents, chatbots, and autonomous systems that use generative AI to search and synthesize information. As AI agents become more common, GEO ensures your content is accessible.</p>
					</div>
