						<h3>Content Audit & Analysis</h3>
						<p>Analyze your current content for AI-readability, semantic richness, and comprehensiveness. Identify optimization opportunities for generative AI discovery and synthesis.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="process-arrow">→</div>
					<div class="process-step">
						<div class="step-number">2</div>
