						<p><strong>Goal:</strong> Appear in AI Overviews, featured snippets, voice responses</p>
						<p><strong>Optimization:</strong> Direct answers, schema markup, fact-based content</p>
						<p><strong>User Action:</strong> Sees your brand in AI answers (may or may not click)</p>
					</div>
					<div class="comparison-card">
						<h3>GEO (Generative Engine Optimization)</h3>
						<p><strong>Focus:</strong> Being learned from and synthesized by generative AI</p>
						<p><strong>Goal:</strong> Content included in AI training and synthesis</p>
						<p><strong>Optimization:</strong> Semantic richness, comprehensive coverage, AI-friendly structure</p>
						<p><strong>User Action:</strong> AI learns from your content to generate responses</p>
					</div>
				</div>
