						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-4">
							<span>What platforms does GEO optimize for?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-4">
							<p>GEO optimizes for generative AI systems including ChatGPT, Claude, Google Gemini, Microsoft Copilot, Perplexity, and AI agents that autonomously research and make decisions. The goal is to ensure your content is discovered, learned from, and synthesized by these systems when generating responses.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-5">
