						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-5">
							<p>GEO results depend on when generative AI systems update their training data and knowledge bases. Since these systems learn from web content continuously, you may start seeing your information influence AI responses within 2-4 months, though this varies based on how frequently AI systems update their knowledge and how authoritative your content is.</p>
